hex
Class hexCell

java.lang.Object
  online.game.cell<FINALTYPE>
      online.game.chipCell<hexCell,hexChip>
          hex.hexCell
All Implemented Interfaces:
HexConstants, Digestable, Drawable, UniversalConstants, Play2Constants, PlayConstants
public class hexCell
extends chipCell<hexCell,hexChip>
implements HexConstants

specialized cell used for the game hex, not for all games using a hex board. this uses chipCell which holds only a single chip, but can be switched to stackCell if the chips are ever stackable.

the game hex needs only a single object on each cell, or empty.

Author:
ddyer
See Also:
chipCell, stackCell
